snippet.title: MAD
snippet.description: The outrageous humor and pop culture parodies of MAD magazine come to life in this satirical animated sketch show. See cartoons inspired by classic material like Sergio Aragones, Don Martin and Spy Vs. Spy. Watch full episodes free online videos from MAD at CartoonNetwork.com.
